<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.3">
<l>alamaṉ ṉumaṭal curicaṅ kameṭut taṭalā ḻiyiṉā laṇiyā ruruvil</l>
<l>pulamaṉ ṉuvaṭam puṉaikoṅ kaiyiṉāḷ poṟaitī ramuṉā ḷaṭuvā ḷamaril</l>
<l>palamaṉ ṉarpaṭac cuṭarā ḻiyiṉaip pakalōṉ maṟaiyap paṇikoṇ ṭaṇicēr</l>
<l>nilamaṉ ṉaṉumā yulakāṇ ṭavaṉuk kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for the one who rules the world, having become king</l>
<l rend="indent">of the beautiful earth,</l>
<l>In a jewel-covered form with the battle discus</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] bearing the whorled battle conch which abides in water,</l>
<l>Having made use of the fiery discus to hide the day lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">to end the burdens of the lady on whose necklace-adorned breast</l>
<l rend="indent">the senses fixate,</l>
<l>Long ago when many kings died in the deadly war</l>
<l rend="indent">where men were destroyed, is the great mountain, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
